ğŸ” Example: When to use what
ğŸ‘‰ useState: counter, form field
ğŸ‘‰ useEffect: fetch data from API when component mounts
ğŸ‘‰ useContext: user login status for the whole app
ğŸ‘‰ useRef: focus an input, store previous value
ğŸ‘‰ useCallback: pass a stable function to child to prevent re-render
ğŸ‘‰ useMemo: cache a slow calculation result (e.g., large list filter)

