useReducer = state manager for complex logic, similar to Redux reducer pattern but local to a component.


useReducer is an alternative to useState for managing more complex state logic in React.

Itâ€™s inspired by Redux-style reducers:

You have a state

You have actions

You have a reducer function that decides how to update the state based on the action.